      "content": "I see. I'm a bit concerned about that \"anecdotal\" classification though. I've had internal reports from a few different field attaches that seem fairly consistent regarding troop concentrations. Are you saying those specific reports have been vetted and found unreliable, or are we just not prioritizing them right now?",
